    "In contrast, developing regions may face challenges such as limited access to high-tech resources, varying levels of digital literacy, and reduced exposure to AI-driven tools.",
    "These disparities may impact how students and educators interact with AI in education, shaping diverse experiences and outcomes depending on regional access and familiarity with these technologies (Viberg et al., 2024; Yang et al., 2024).",
    "The context of this study was an introductory programming course, a mandatory offering during the 2023-2024 Fall Semester.",
    "The course was taught across three sections by the same instructor, who is also one of the authors, over the span of 14 weeks.",
    "All course materials were provided through the university's Moodle-based learning management system (LMS)."
  ],
